Package: ec.europa.eu
Title: Eurostat Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Eurostat SDMX API at ec.europa.eu.
    Covers GDP, unemployment, inflation, and dataset search across ~8,000
    Eurostat datasets. Includes LLM context injection via estat_context().
